Put their trust, 
Put their trust 
Under the shadow of thy wings. 
{2x paragraph}

They shall be abundantly satisfied. {3x}
With the fullness of thine house
And thou shall make them drink of the rivers of thy pleasure.  {2x} 
{2x paragraph}

